# HSM collector conformance — alert registration (AddOrUpdateSensorRequest Alerts/TtlAlerts).
# The alert builder is staged then consumed by a create_*_with_alerts verb (alerts must be known
# at sensor creation). Enum args are the numeric values of the managed
# AlertCombination/AlertProperty/AlertOperation/TargetType/AlertDestinationMode/AlertIcon enums.
# New verbs:
# alert_new|kind                                   (instant | bar | ttl)
# alert_condition|combination|property|operation|target_type[|value]   (value omitted/ignored for LastValue=1)
# alert_notification|template|destination_mode
# alert_icon|icon                                  (managed AlertIcon -> UTF-8 emoji)
# alert_sensor_error                               (raises alert Status to Error)
# alert_confirmation|period_ms
# alert_inactivity|period_ms                       (TTL alert: feeds TTLs/TtlAlerts)
# alert_disabled
# alert_stage                                      (finalize current alert into the pending list)
# create_int_sensor_with_alerts|path|ttl_ms|unit|description    (consumes the pending alerts)
# Contract notes:
# - Alerts serialize as the real AlertUpdateRequest (numeric enums; AlertIcon.Warning -> the emoji
#   escaped by the default encoder to \u26A0; ConfirmationPeriod in ticks; LastValue target Value is
#   null). The bytes are also pinned by the paired WireFormatGoldenLockTests / native
#   NativeWireRegistrationWithAlertsMatchesNetByteLayout.
# - A TTL alert (IfInactivityPeriodIs) lands in TtlAlerts and its inactivity drives TTLTicks.

instant_alert_registers_in_payload|create_collector
instant_alert_registers_in_payload|alert_new|instant
instant_alert_registers_in_payload|alert_condition|0|20|2|0|42
instant_alert_registers_in_payload|alert_sensor_error
instant_alert_registers_in_payload|alert_notification|spike|200
instant_alert_registers_in_payload|alert_icon|1
instant_alert_registers_in_payload|alert_stage
instant_alert_registers_in_payload|alert_new|ttl
instant_alert_registers_in_payload|alert_inactivity|60000
instant_alert_registers_in_payload|alert_notification|inactive|3
instant_alert_registers_in_payload|alert_stage
instant_alert_registers_in_payload|create_int_sensor_with_alerts|contract/alert/basic|0|3|d
instant_alert_registers_in_payload|start
instant_alert_registers_in_payload|stop
instant_alert_registers_in_payload|expect_registration_count|1
instant_alert_registers_in_payload|expect_registration_contains|0|"Alerts":[{"Conditions":[{"Combination":0,"Operation":2,"Property":20,"Target":{"Type":0,"Value":"42"}}],"Status":3,"DestinationMode":200,"Template":"spike","Icon":"\u26A0","IsDisabled":false,"ConfirmationPeriod":null,"ScheduledNotificationTime":null,"ScheduledRepeatMode":null,"ScheduledInstantSend":null}]
instant_alert_registers_in_payload|expect_registration_contains|0|"TtlAlerts":[{"Conditions":[],"Status":1,"DestinationMode":3,"Template":"inactive","Icon":null,"IsDisabled":false,"ConfirmationPeriod":null,"ScheduledNotificationTime":null,"ScheduledRepeatMode":null,"ScheduledInstantSend":null}]
instant_alert_registers_in_payload|expect_registration_contains|0|"TTLTicks":[600000000]

